{"tid":1006234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"安倍晉三喺銀座商店街體驗Cashless付款","createTime":"2019-02-02T20:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T20:24:18.000Z","uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"894ed24afecc9ddc9e67778f2a00dca347723c75","tid":1006234,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T20:24:18.000Z","msg":"喺Twitter見到啲咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sekohiroshige/status/1091581068946231296?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsekohiroshige%2Fstatus%2F1091581068946231296%3Fs%3D21&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7i%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=cbc6ed10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsekohiroshige%2Fstatus%2F1091581068946231296%3Fs%3D21&h=5244799f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sekohiroshige/status/1091581068946231296?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PMU2TQa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPMU2TQa.png&h=e8c08a6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">首先去7-11申請咗張Nanaco 順便增值</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ooz2TQi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fooz2TQi.png&h=7fe0dbad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">然後去咗商店街魚檔用Nanaco畀錢買魚刺身</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dPnTf3H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdPnTf3H.png&h=8ce1cb4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好似遲下有計劃，只要用電子付款包括信用卡、IC卡、QR Code會有優惠，圖中為預計嘅宣傳Poster</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S5kUKXx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS5kUKXx.png&h=e95320c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXpm9pd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXpm9pd.png&h=2e0dfda8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">之後再去花店買嘢，今次用嘅係Qr Code嘅Paypay</span><br />\n<br />\n睇返日本網民留言，似乎對電子付款仲有唔少抗拒...<br />\n除咗講地震天災嗰陣唔用得之外，最大問題係IC卡種類太多，例如購物系嘅Edy、Nanaco用唔到嚟坐車，做唔到一卡走天涯。而且一般地方商店都唔接受IC卡，唔夠普及。"}]}